<H2><A NAME="SECTION02402000000000000000"></A><A NAME="1918"></A>
<BR>
最尤推定

</H2>

<P>
尤度(likelihood<A NAME="1919"></A>)を最大にするパラメータを最尤推定量という．<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
l(\theta)=\log p\left(  X|\theta\right)  =\sum\log p\left(  X_{i}%
|\theta\right)
\end{displaymath}
 -->
<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<IMG
 WIDTH="248" HEIGHT="41" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img504.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle l(\theta)=\log p\left( X\vert\theta\right) =\sum\log p\left( X_{i}%
\vert\theta\right)
$">
</DIV><P></P>
例&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ポアソン分布の場合<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><TABLE CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="RIGHT"><IMG
 WIDTH="30" HEIGHT="31" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img505.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle l(\theta)$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="144" HEIGHT="60" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img506.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\sum_{i=1}^{n}\log p\left( X_{i}\vert\theta,\Delta\right)$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="158" HEIGHT="60" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img507.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\sum_{i=1}^{n}\log\frac{\left( \theta\Delta\right) ^{X_{i}}}{X_{i}%
!}e^{-\theta\Delta}$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="237" HEIGHT="60" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img508.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\sum_{i=1}^{n}[X_{i}\log\left( \theta\Delta\right) -\theta\Delta-\log X_{i}!]$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
</TABLE></DIV>
<BR CLEAR="ALL"><P></P>
最尤推定は<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><TABLE CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="RIGHT"><IMG
 WIDTH="43" HEIGHT="53" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img509.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle \frac{\partial l(\theta)}{\partial\theta}$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="108" HEIGHT="60" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img510.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\sum_{i=1}^{n}[\frac{X_{i}%
}{\theta}-\Delta]$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="126" HEIGHT="55" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img511.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_{i}}{\theta}-n\Delta$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
</TABLE></DIV>
<BR CLEAR="ALL"><P></P>
<!-- MATH
 $\frac{\partial l(\theta)}{\partial\theta}=0$
 -->
<IMG
 WIDTH="65" HEIGHT="40" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img512.gif"
 ALT="$ \frac{\partial l(\theta)}{\partial\theta}=0$">より<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
\hat{\theta}_{n}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_{i}}{n\Delta}=\frac{\bar{X}}{\Delta}%
\end{displaymath}
 -->
<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<IMG
 WIDTH="144" HEIGHT="55" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img513.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle \hat{\theta}_{n}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}X_{i}}{n\Delta}=\frac{\bar{X}}{\Delta}%
$">
</DIV><P></P>
ただし平均値<!-- MATH
 $\bar{X}=\frac{1}{n}\sum
X_{i}$
 -->
<IMG
 WIDTH="92" HEIGHT="34" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img514.gif"
 ALT="$ \bar{X}=\frac{1}{n}\sum
X_{i}$">

<P>
最尤推定値の期待値は<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
E\hat{\theta}_{n}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}EX_{i}}{n\Delta}=\theta
\end{displaymath}
 -->
<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<IMG
 WIDTH="159" HEIGHT="55" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img515.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle E\hat{\theta}_{n}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}EX_{i}}{n\Delta}=\theta
$">
</DIV><P></P>
分散は<P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><TABLE CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="100%" ALIGN="CENTER">
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="RIGHT"><IMG
 WIDTH="101" HEIGHT="38" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img516.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle E(\hat{\theta}_{n}-E\hat{\theta}_{n})^{2}$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="151" HEIGHT="61" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img517.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =E\left[ \frac{\sum_{i=1}%
^{n}X_{i}}{n\Delta}-\theta\right] ^{2}$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="187" HEIGHT="60" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img518.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\frac{1}{(n\Delta)^{2}}\sum_{i=1}^{n}E(X_{i}-\Delta\theta)^{2}$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="MIDDLE">
<TD>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD NOWRAP ALIGN="LEFT"><IMG
 WIDTH="48" HEIGHT="51" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img519.gif"
 ALT="$\displaystyle =\frac{\theta}{n\Delta}%
$"></TD>
<TD NOWRAP WIDTH="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</TD></TR>
</TABLE></DIV>
<BR CLEAR="ALL"><P></P>
最後の等式にはポアソン分布の性質<!-- MATH
 $E(X_{i}-\Delta\theta)^{2}=EX_{i}=\Delta\theta$
 -->
<IMG
 WIDTH="190" HEIGHT="33" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img520.gif"
 ALT="$ E(X_{i}-\Delta\theta)^{2}=EX_{i}=\Delta\theta$">を用いた.

